1. In your AWS console, click **Route 53**.

1. In the left hand navigation, click on **Hosted Zones**.

1. Click on **Create Hosted Zone**.

1. Enter a fully qualified domain name.

	<%= image_tag 'cloudform/create_hosted_zone.png' %>

1. Click **Create**.

1. Find the domain you created in the previous step and click on **Create Record Set**.

1. **Edit the Record Set** by creating a **Name**. Specify the IP in the **Value** field.

    <%= image_tag 'cloudform/delegated_domain.png' %> 

1. Click **Create**.

1. The fully qualified domain name appears in your **Hosted Zone** dashboard.

	<%= image_tag 'cloudform/hosted_zone_dashboard.png' %> 


